      • transitionOf

        public static Transition transitionOf(char ref,
                                      char call)
        Gets a the enum representing the transition from a 'reference' to a 'call' base.

        For example, a transtion from 'A' to 'T' would return AtoT.

        Parameters:
        ref - reference base (one of of {A, C, T, G}).
        call - call base (one of of {A, C, T, G}).
        Returns:
        enum representation for the transition.
